Merrin Dungey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Merrin_Dungey 0 Merrin Melissa Dungey (born August 6, 1971) is an American film and television actress, known for her roles on the television series The King of Queens, Alias, ‘’Malcolm in the Middle’’, and Summerland. Dungey also appeared as Ursula on Once Upon a Time, and starred in the legal drama Conviction. Most recently, she appeared on the medical drama The Resident, and will costar in the 2019 legal drama The Fix.
